text: José Javier Eguiguren Ríofrío (3 December 1816 - 1884) was acting President of Ecuador from 6 October 1875 to 9 December 1875. Eguiguren was born in 3 December 1816 in Ibarra, Ecuador. He died in 1884 in Quito, Ecuador. ==Other websites== * Official Website of the Ecuadorian Government about the country President's History Category:1816 births Category:1884 deaths Category:Presidents of Ecuador
